@node "System" "System Vorraussetzungen"

  To use dA cOOL bOOTER you need at least an Amiga (oh, can`t I use
  it on PeeZee ?) with harddisk and OS2.0.

  dA cOOL bOOTER needs also the reqtools.library (© by Niço François)
  in libs:. Get this library from Aminet or me.

  Additionally you must have the workbench installed on your harddisk.

@endnode

@node "ques" "Starting a game/demo"

  It`s so easy.......

  I`ll explain it to your in three simple steps:

  1) Start dA cOOL bOOTER
  2) Select a script/executable to boot

  THAT WAS IT! ALL IS DONE! Now start the game/demo and @{"register" link "register}.

  If you`re a registered user you can click the "Create script"
  button for get a starter installed.

  Legend: Script: Script is a standard Amiga DOS script as used by
                  IconX or execute. Note: everything what`s not
                  executable will be identified as script, because
                  scripts don`t have a special header
        
          Executable: Standard Amiga DOS executable.
  
@endnode

@node "history" "History"

  V1.0: (Freeware Release Version)

  - controlled by CLI
  - only scripts are supported

  V1.1: (Freeware Release Version)

  - fatal bug fixed

  V1.2: (Freeware Release Version)

  - now executable support
  - simple docs

  V1.3: (Shareware Release Version)

  - added nice GUI
  - reqtools.library (© by Niço François) supported by the GUI
  - AmigaGuide® documentation

  V1.4: (Shareware Release Version)
 
  - now keyfile support (not so good system, will change in near future)
  - bugs removed
  

  Future plans:

  - more options
  - your plan -> contact @{"me" link "autor"}

@endnode

@node "Cardware" "Shareware"

  This program is Shareware. If you like & use it @{"register" link "register"}  yourself by
  sending $15 (20DM) with the filled-in @{"Registration form" link "register"} to
  @{"this" link "autor"} adress. You`ll get a keyfile which enables the disabled options.
  So you have a lot more @{"features" link "option"}.

  Additionally I`m interested in errors or suggestions to dA cOOL bOOTER.
  Take a look @{"here" link "autor"}.    
@endnode

@node "why" "Was bringt mir die Vollversion?"

 The fullversion (=@{"keyfile" link "key"}) features:

 1. get a starter installed 
 2. don`t type 13x "I WILL REGISTER NOW" in till the game starts

 and more because of the future versions which run with the @{"keyfile" link "key"} undisabled,
 of course.

 @{"Register" link "register"} now.

@endnode

